# Ignore everything by default
*

# Un-ignore essential root metadata files
!.gitignore
!LICENSE
!CHANGELOG.md
!README.md

# Un-ignore documentation files (moved to root)
!portfolio-overview.md
!technical-deep-dive.md
!design-system.md
!performance-seo-analytics.md

# Explicitly ignore everything else (code, config, assets)
admin/
blog/
landing/
portfolio/
shared/
.well-known/
firebase.json
firestore.indexes.json
firestore.rules
.htaccess
index.html
favicon.svg
robots.txt
sitemap.xml
*.zip
node_modules/
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
